1031
01:05:56,953 --> 01:06:00,414
-He had this bushy bang.
-I see.

1032
01:06:00,498 --> 01:06:03,417
And he was wearing a dress shirt
with sweatsuit pants.

1033
01:06:04,418 --> 01:06:06,796
-Was this the jacket too?
-Yes.

1034
01:06:07,463 --> 01:06:09,966
He looked at me
after he withdrew the money,

1035
01:06:10,049 --> 01:06:11,592
so I stared back.

1036
01:06:12,176 --> 01:06:14,136
Did you see where he went?

1037
01:06:15,888 --> 01:06:17,807
I wouldn't know.

1038
01:06:18,599 --> 01:06:21,686
I saw him catching a taxi.

1039
01:06:22,937 --> 01:06:24,021
A taxi?

1040
01:06:24,105 --> 01:06:28,567
<i>A female university student in Gunpo
has been missing for 18 days,</i>

1041
01:06:28,651 --> 01:06:30,903
<i>so the police began an open search.</i>

1042
01:06:30,987 --> 01:06:34,448
{\an8}<i>The police obtained footage
of a man in his twenties to thirties</i>

1043
01:06:34,532 --> 01:06:39,078
{\an8}<i>withdrawing 700,000 won
with this woman's debit card at a bank.</i>

1044
01:06:39,161 --> 01:06:42,415
{\an8}<i>He's now openly wanted as the key suspect.</i>

1045
01:06:42,498 --> 01:06:44,542
Yes, all right.

1046
01:06:46,252 --> 01:06:47,878
I checked with the taxi company,

1047
01:06:47,962 --> 01:06:50,172
and they haven't found the driver yet.

1048
01:06:50,256 --> 01:06:53,676
If he took a taxi,
he probably lives near the bank.

1049
01:06:53,759 --> 01:06:55,761
The bank is close to where
she went missing.

1050
01:06:56,345 --> 01:07:00,016
It won't be easy,
but let's check every security camera

1051
01:07:00,099 --> 01:07:03,185
on the streets from the missing point
to the bank.

1052
01:07:05,730 --> 01:07:09,442
We'll check every footage
within six kilometers of the bank.

1053
01:07:09,525 --> 01:07:10,901
Everything?

1054
01:07:10,985 --> 01:07:13,320
There are at least
over 300 cameras out there.

1055
01:07:13,988 --> 01:07:15,281
Yes, we'll check everything.

1056
01:07:15,364 --> 01:07:16,365
Please cooperate.

1057
01:07:16,449 --> 01:07:17,908
-Okay.
-Okay.

1058
01:07:22,705 --> 01:07:24,040
Right here.

1059
01:07:29,336 --> 01:07:30,546
What were you doing then?

1060
01:07:31,922 --> 01:07:33,841
I was at home.

1061
01:07:39,221 --> 01:07:40,806
Darn it.

1062
01:07:45,019 --> 01:07:46,270
Let's keep trying.

1063
01:07:53,277 --> 01:07:54,737
Gyeonggi 89.

1064
01:07:57,073 --> 01:07:58,866
-Thank you.
-You're welcome.

1065
01:08:11,170 --> 01:08:12,213
Hold on.

1066
01:08:13,130 --> 01:08:15,591
Could you rewind the footage just now?

1067
01:08:17,384 --> 01:08:19,845
Yes. That one. Please zoom in.

1068
01:08:25,893 --> 01:08:28,187
-Chief Kook. Come over here.
-Yes?

1069
01:09:06,976 --> 01:09:09,895
STAY TUNED FOR THE EPILOGUE

1070
01:09:34,879 --> 01:09:36,046
Gosh.

1071
01:09:36,755 --> 01:09:40,134
I've been working in the force
for about 30 years.

1072
01:09:40,718 --> 01:09:41,802
And in my opinion,

1073
01:09:42,845 --> 01:09:46,932
you're the best cop in Korea.

1074
01:09:48,309 --> 01:09:50,227
That was out of the blue.

1075
01:09:50,853 --> 01:09:53,564
I've never seen you second guess yourself.

1076
01:09:53,647 --> 01:09:56,483
You only focus on your job.
You don't let the job get to you.

1077
01:09:57,109 --> 01:09:59,486
So for the past 20 years,
I have been watching you

1078
01:09:59,570 --> 01:10:01,947
doing so well without much trouble.

1079
01:10:02,031 --> 01:10:08,162
And I realized that people like you
were born to be police officers.

1080
01:10:08,245 --> 01:10:11,290
And I was proud to have
a competent junior like you.

1081
01:10:12,875 --> 01:10:15,628
But the guy you scouted, Song Ha-young,

1082
01:10:16,378 --> 01:10:17,922
is just like you.

1083
01:10:18,005 --> 01:10:19,882
He reminds me of you in every sense.

1084
01:10:19,965 --> 01:10:22,551
How does he remind you of me?

1085
01:10:23,552 --> 01:10:28,182
Ha-young is young, handsome,

1086
01:10:28,849 --> 01:10:30,392
and looks great with a perm.

1087
01:10:33,312 --> 01:10:35,147
You two can't see it.

1088
01:10:35,773 --> 01:10:37,483
But in other people's eyes,

1089
01:10:38,067 --> 01:10:40,236
Kook Young-soo and Song Ha-youngâ€¦

1090
01:10:41,820 --> 01:10:42,863
are the same.

1091
01:10:45,241 --> 01:10:47,243
So that got me worried all of a sudden.

1092
01:10:47,993 --> 01:10:49,119
Worried about whom?

1093
01:10:49,203 --> 01:10:51,205
Isn't it obvious? It's you.

1094
01:10:51,288 --> 01:10:53,582
Why? I'm a grown man.

1095
01:10:57,920 --> 01:11:01,173
It's easy to come back
after running away once.

1096
01:11:02,591 --> 01:11:03,676
Butâ€¦

1097
01:11:04,885 --> 01:11:07,471
two people who never
thought about running away

1098
01:11:09,598 --> 01:11:12,017
ended up working together.

1099
01:11:12,101 --> 01:11:13,852
So I was worried thatâ€¦

1100
01:11:16,563 --> 01:11:18,983
both of you might give up
if one of you crumbled down.

1101
01:11:23,654 --> 01:11:25,072
You do have a point.

1102
01:11:28,409 --> 01:11:29,868
That's how I feel right now.

1103
01:11:32,871 --> 01:11:35,499
Just like you said,
I've been wrong for the last 20 years.

1104
01:11:38,252 --> 01:11:40,671
It doesn't feel like
I've been focusing on my job.

1105
01:11:43,173 --> 01:11:45,134
Because I was too busy with my job,

1106
01:11:46,593 --> 01:11:48,929
perhaps I failed to
take care of those around me.

1107
01:11:50,931 --> 01:11:53,767
And I wonder if I've been
doing it wrong the whole time.

1108
01:11:56,186 --> 01:11:57,396
Young-soo.

1109
01:12:00,316 --> 01:12:02,943
Cops are human too.

1110
01:12:08,324 --> 01:12:09,992
Get in. I had fun today.

1111
01:12:10,075 --> 01:12:12,328
-Let's grab one more drink.
-We've had enough.

1112
01:12:13,787 --> 01:12:16,081
-Sir, please drive him home safely.
-Sure.

1113
01:12:16,165 --> 01:12:17,708
Apartment Complex Seven in Mok-dong.

1114
01:12:18,208 --> 01:12:20,252
-You can go.
-One more drink.

1115
01:12:20,336 --> 01:12:21,795
-Bye.
-Wait.

1116
01:12:21,879 --> 01:12:23,088
One more!

1117
01:12:25,257 --> 01:12:26,800
Thanks, Gil-pyo!

1118
01:12:39,480 --> 01:12:40,606
Woo Ho-sung?

1119
01:12:41,190 --> 01:12:42,649
You wanted to see me?

1120
01:12:42,733 --> 01:12:45,027
<i>Can we talk at the station?</i>

1121
01:12:45,110 --> 01:12:47,363
<i>Are you suspecting me?
Do you have evidence?</i>

1122
01:12:47,446 --> 01:12:50,449
We can't let this guy buy time.
He'll destroy all the evidence.

1123
01:12:50,532 --> 01:12:51,867
<i>This bastard is unbelievable.</i>

1124
01:12:51,950 --> 01:12:53,494
<i>What if I'm not the culprit?</i>

1125
01:12:53,577 --> 01:12:55,871
<i>I'm sure he was psychologically pressured.</i>

1126
01:12:58,499 --> 01:13:00,209
-Who's calling?
-This is Woo Ho-sung.

